    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>Your information is used for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>To provide and maintain our app and services.</li>
        <li>To communicate with you, including sending notifications or updates regarding your account.</li>
        <li>To analyze usage patterns and improve the functionality and performance of the app.</li>
        <li>To ensure safety and compliance with regulatory requirements (e.g., safety checks, vehicle inspections).</li>
        <li>To prevent fraud, abuse, and misuse of the app.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your information in the following circumstances:</p>
